<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<bug>
    <id>HHH-10210</id>
    <title>Wrong escape of [ and ] chars</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">I've this @Formula annotation in my entity bean:</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">{code:java}
@Formula(value = "(SELECT DATE_ADD(v.dataAndata, [INTERVAL] v.minutiTrasportoAndata [MINUTE]) FROM VenditaB2B v WHERE v.id = id)")
{code}</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">Unfortunately seems that Hibernate don't escape [ and ] chars so the native query is wrong because [ and ] are still present in the final query.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="4">
            <sentence id="4.1">I think this is a bug because @Formula should escape that chars as the @Column annotation does.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
